s://apps.apple.com/app/apple-store/id804728901?pt=423641&amp;ct=mobile_page&amp;mt=8" rel="noopener" aria-label="Download our app on the App Store for iOS devices."></a><a class="g-play" target="_blank" href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.zoho.campaigns&amp;referrer=utm_source=campaigns_mobile_page&amp;utm_medium=appbadge&amp;utm_campaign=campaigns_mobile_page" rel="noopener" aria-label="Download our app on Google Play for Android devices."></a></div><div class="email-creative"><picture><source srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACwAAAAAAQABAAA=" data-srcset="//www.zohowebstatic.com/sites/zweb/images/campaigns/ipad.webp" type="image/webp"><img class="tab-creative" width="732" height="561" alt="Zoho Campaigns dashboard on devices" data-lazy data-src="//www.zohowebstatic.com/sites/zweb/images/campaigns/ipad.png" src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20viewBox%3D%22100%25%20100%25%20200%20150%22%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E"></picture><span class="lft-creative"><img width="250" alt="Zoho Campaigns dashboard on devices" data-lazy data-src="//www.zohowebstatic.com/sites/zweb/images/campaigns/iphone.png" height="454" src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20viewBox%3D%22100%25%20100%25%20200%20150%22%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E" aria-hidden="true"></span><span class="rtr-creative" aria-hidden="true"><picture><source srcset="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACwAAAAAAQABAAA=" data-srcset="//www.zohowebstatic.com/sites/zweb/images/campaigns/android.webp" type="image/webp"><img width="220" alt="Android" data-lazy data-src="//www.zohowebstatic.com/sites/zweb/images/campaigns/android.png" height="449" src="data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf8,%3Csvg%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%20viewBox%3D%22100%25%20100%25%20200%20150%22%3E%3C%2Fsvg%3E" aria-hidden="true"></picture></span></div></div></div><div class="common-section faq-section"><div class="content-wrap"><h2 class="head-txt">Frequently asked questions</h2><div class="pricing-faq"><ul class="zfaqWrapper"><li class="zfaq-wrap active"><button aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="answer1" id="question1">What's the difference between Zoho Campaigns and Zoho Mail? <span class="arrow">&nbsp;</span></button><div class="faq-content" id="answer1" role="region" aria-labelledby="question1" style="display: block;"><p>Zoho Campaigns, an email service provider (ESP), is built to help businesses send marketing emails in bulk on a lawful basis. <a href="/mail/">Zoho Mail</a>, an inbox service provider (ISP), is designed for teams and organizations to run and manage their professional communications.</p></div></li><li class="zfaq-wrap"><button aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="answer2" id="question2">What's the difference between Zoho Campaigns and Zoho Marketing Automation? <span class="arrow">&nbsp;</span></button><div class="faq-content" id="answer2" role="region" aria-labelledby="question2"><p>Zoho Campaigns is a platform built exclusively for email marketing—you bring in and manage the email database of your leads and contacts and send marketing emails to them. Zoho Marketing Automation is a platform that lets you capture leads from your website, nurture them across channels like email, SMS, and social media, and convert them. Principally, the latter is a single place where you can run and automate your entire marketing.</p></div></li><li class="zfaq-wrap"><button aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="answer3" id="question3">Can I send transactional emails through Zoho Campaigns? <span class="arrow">&nbsp;</span></button><div class="faq-content" id="answer3" role="region" aria-labelledby="question3"><p>No, Zoho Campaigns only allows you to send marketing emails. For transactional emails, we suggest that you try <a href="/zeptomail/?src=zchome_faq">ZeptoMail</a>, our in-house transactional email service.</p></div></li><li class="zfaq-wrap"><button aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="answer4" id="question4">How does Zoho Campaigns help in my email marketing efforts? <span class="arrow">&nbsp;</span></button><div class="faq-content" id="answer4" role="region" aria-labelledby="question4"><p>Zoho Campaigns is built in a way to facilitate every stage of your email marketing. It lets you import, export, and organically grow your mailing lists. The presence of customizable, readymade <a href="/campaigns/features/email-templates.html">email templates</a> means you can quickly design your content. It also has smart scheduling options that ensure your emails reach your recipients in a way and at the time you want them to.</p><p>What's more, you can even automate your entire email marketing using <a href="/campaigns/marketing-automation/email-workflow.html">workflows</a>. Simply drag and drop the pre-built components that suit your requirements, define the content and send time, and you are set.</p></div></li><li class="zfaq-wrap"><button aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="answer5" id="question5">Are emails sent through Zoho Campaigns responsive? <span class="arrow">&nbsp;</span></button><div class="faq-content" id="answer5" role="region" aria-labelledby="question5"><p>Yes, the <a href="/campaigns/newsletter-templates.html">newsletter templates</a> of Zoho Campaigns are coded in a way that they dynamically adjust to the display size of different devices.</p></div></li><li class="zfaq-wrap"><button aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="answer6" id="question6">Can I clean my mailing lists using Zoho Campaigns? <span class="arrow">&nbsp;</span></button><div class="faq-content" id="answer6" role="region" aria-labelledby="question6"><p>No, Zoho Campaigns helps you manage your contacts, including bounces and unsubscribes. To identify and remove invalid contacts, we suggest that you try a third-party service.</p></div></li><li class="zfaq-wrap"><button aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="answer7" id="question7">Can I tie my email marketing and sales together using Zoho Campaigns? <span class="arrow">&nbsp;</span></button><div class="faq-content" id="answer7" role="region" aria-labelledby="question7"><p>Yes, Zoho Campaigns integrates with CRMs like Zoho CRM, Bigin by Zoho CRM, HubSpot, Salesforce, MS Dynamics 365, and Sugar CRM to ensure sales and email marketing goes hand in hand.</p></div></li><li class="zfaq-wrap"><button aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="answer8" id="question8">Do you offer dedicated IPs? <span class="arrow">&nbsp;</span></button><div class="faq-content" id="answer8" role="region" aria-labelledby="question8"><p>Yes, we do. Wanting to send more than 100,000 emails per month or 50,000 per week and requiring total control of the email-sending IP are some of the reasons we suggest that you consider a dedicated IP. It has to be purchased separately. You can request one by filling out the form embedded <a class="nonlang" href="/campaigns/dedicated-ip-address.html">on this page</a>.</p></div></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="bottom-cta-section"><div class="content-wrap"><h2>Unleash the power of email marketing with Zoho Campaigns.</h2><a href="/campaigns/signup.html" class="act-btn cta-btn">Sign up for free</a></div></div> </main> <footer><div class="zw-product-footer"></div><div class="zw-global-footer"></div><div class="zw-only-copyright"></div><div class="zw-promo-bottom"></div> </footer> <aside><div class="zw-other-info"></div> </aside><script src="//www.zohowebstatic.com/sites/zweb/js/common/zcms.js"></script><script src="//www.zohowebstatic.com/sites/zweb/js/common/validation-plugin.js"></script><script src="//www.zohowebstatic.com/sites/zweb/js/common/slick-plugin.js"></script><script src="//www.zohowebstatic.com/sites/zweb/js/common/zohocustom.js"></script><script src="//www.zohowebstatic.com/sites/zweb/js/product/campaigns.js"></script><script src="//www.zohowebstatic.com/sites/zweb/js/translation/campaigns/2316.js"></script></body></html>